      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TWO STAR MIKADO (7) has finished in the placings both career runs so far, the latest when second (17.26) at this track. Overdue for a win and looks hard to beat here. CHILLI JAM (1) was on speed settling but found some traffic when checked, missing the frame to finish seventh (24.29) at Geelong in a Rank Limit - Maiden. Better than last start and can bounce back. TAKE A RHINO (2) is still a maiden after eight runs but rarely far away, the latest filling a minor placing when second at this track. Gave a huge sight last time and went down narrowly. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Expected to be in the finish again. AURORA SKY FORCE (8) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
